{"title":"【085】CSS布局之之浮动基础","slug":"hell0-world31","date":"2022-10-24T12:50:27.000Z","updated":"2023-06-21T11:21:39.515Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/hell0-world31.json","photos":[],"link":"","excerpt":"                flow                <br><br><br>    容器自上而下纵向排列","covers":null,"content":"<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta http-equiv=\"X-UA-Compatible\" content=\"IE=edge\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"wclassth=device-wclassth, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>flow</title>\n    <link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"flow-style.css\">\n</head>\n<body>\n   <div class=\"box1\"></div> \n   <div class=\"box2\"></div> \n   <div class=\"box3\"></div> <br><br><br>\n    容器自上而下纵向排列<span id=\"more\"></span>,符合页面容器普通文档的排列规则.如果想要横向排列,可运用样式的元素类型知识,通过转换元素的类型,实现这样的横向显示效果.<br><br>\n    将这些容器设置浮动样式float:left/right/none;<br><br>\n    容器浮动后会脱离标准文档流，相当于飘起来了。<br><br>\n    实现多个容器横向排列，只需给所有的容器添加float属性<br><br>\n    <div>\n        <ul>\n            <li>语文</li>\n            <li>数学</li>\n            <li>政治</li>\n            <li>历史</li>\n            <li>地理</li>\n            <li>英语</li>\n        </ul>\n    </div><br><br><br>\n</body>\n</html>","categories":[{"name":"CSS","slug":"CSS","count":30,"path":"api/categories/CSS.json"}],"tags":[]}